[ Jarod &amp; Rita Cobb ] have been falsely accusing us of selling them tampered fertilizer. We did sell them fertilizer, but there was nothing wrong about it. To make things worse, they stole some of our farming equipment.

When their foolish fight against the Weaver family didn't do anything but paint all of us look like ungrateful whiners, they clearly thought they could just cash in on a quick scam and disappear.

