                      <CanPutItems>true</CanPutItems>
                      <Items>
                        <MyObjectBuilder_InventoryItem>
                          <Amount>1</Amount>
                          <PhysicalContent xsi:type="MyObjectBuilder_Datapad">
                            <SubtypeName>Datapad</SubtypeName>
                            <Name>[ Sunset Valley News ]---[ 2/4 ]---[ Pioneers of Farming ]</Name>
                            <Data>[ Pioneers of Farming ]

When you think about fresh, locally grown food, the Weaver family is most likely the first thing that comes into mind. Being the primary supplier of fresh food in Sunset Valley since its colonization.

Today, Governor Benton awarded Ismael and Amy Weaver the "Frontier Spirit medal" for their dedication in pushing Sunset Valley to become fully self-sustained in the future.

While most do appreciate this gesture, the new generation of farmers [ Jarod &amp; Nita Cobb ], [ Rashad &amp; Nadia Hahn ] as well as [ Leroy Holloway ] have raised concerns that most of the monetary aid for farmers goes to one address. One that wouldn't even need the aid.

[ Owen Quin ]---[ Sunset Valley News ]</Data>
                          </PhysicalContent>
                          <ItemId>0</ItemId>
                        </MyObjectBuilder_InventoryItem>
                        <MyObjectBuilder_InventoryItem>
                          <Amount>350</Amount>
                          <PhysicalContent xsi:type="MyObjectBuilder_PhysicalObject">
